data.description: Welcome to Harvard Terrace! This home is in close proximity to the Toledo Zoo, Walbridge Park, Wixies Bakery, Lickity Split, and Toledo Public Dog Park. This home boast original hardwood flooring on the first floor, built-in cabinetry/buffet in the living & dining rooms, granite kitchen countertops, updated cabinetry, newer kitchen appliances, and a bonus family room on the rear of the house due to a converted garage space. This home has historical charm & decor make it yours! The property is being sold As Is.
